prompt: A group of diverse startup founders celebrating their success in a modern office environment. The background features a sleek wooden table and comfortable chairs, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere.

A man in a cozy home office, sitting at a wooden desk with a steaming cup of coffee. The room has warm lighting, with a large window showing a garden view. He is focused on drawing diagrams on a whiteboard, surrounded by books and plants.

A man relaxing in a modern coworking space lounge. He is sitting on a comfortable sofa with a friendly dog beside him. The lounge is stylishly decorated with contemporary furniture and green plants. A small startup team is gathered around a large wooden table in a cozy, contemporary office space. They are collaborating on website designs, with paper sketches and laptops open. A confident startup founder posing for a headshot in a modern office environment. The office is sleek and contemporary, with large windows allowing natural light to pour in. The founder is dressed in smart-casual attire, exuding professionalism and approachability. The background features tasteful office furniture and decor, creating a harmonious and inspiring workspace.

A cheerful startup founder sitting at a shared table in a coworking space, surrounded by other professionals. The founder is smiling warmly, exuding enthusiasm and positivity.
